OL,7,FFirefighters have been let down by
OL,8,Fsenior management who may not
OL,9,Funderstand the scale of problems
OL,10,Ffacing the service, according to a
OL,11,Fcommittee of politicians.
OL,13,FThe Senedd's equality and social
OL,14,Fjustice committee's report, titled
OL,15,F"sound the alarm", outlines a long
OL,16,Flist of concerns about the governance
OL,17,Fof fire and rescue services in Wales.
