OL,5,Cleadership'
OL,7,FIt accuses senior officials of
OL,8,F"downplaying" bullying allegations
OL,9,Fagainst the of South Wales Fire and
OL,10,FRescue Service, Stuart Millington. He
OL,11,Fdenies the allegations.
OL,13,FThe report also asks serious questions
OL,14,Fabout how complaints are handled and
OL,15,Fsuggests senior bosses may want to
OL,16,F"reflect on their positions".
