OL,7,FOver the last four months, ITV Cymru
OL,8,FWales has been investigating claims of
OL,9,F"toxic cultures" at the services in ,
OL,10,Fand Mid and West Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,11,FService.
OL,13,FMore than 35 whistleblowers in north
OL,14,FWales told us when they complained,
OL,15,Fnothing was done.
OL,17,FSome of those whistleblowers have now
OL,18,Fdescribed the report's contents as
OL,19,F"shocking but not surprising".
