OL,7,FSince January, the equality and social
OL,8,Fjustice committee has been
OL,9,Finvestigating the governance of Wales'
OL,10,Ffire and rescue services.
OL,12,FThe committee, made up of MSs from a
OL,13,Fvariety of different parties, has
OL,14,Fheard evidence from a range of senior
OL,15,Ffigures in Wales' fire services
OL,16,Fincluding Dawn Docx, the chief fire
OL,17,Fofficer of North Wales Fire Service.
