OL,5,Cleadership'
OL,7,FReflecting on the evidence, Jenny
OL,8,FRathbone MS, who chairs the Senedd
OL,9,Fcommittee, said: "We were disturbed by
OL,10,Fhow many people at the top of the
OL,11,Fcurrent governance system didn't seem
OL,12,Fto be aware of how serious the problem
OL,13,Fis."
OL,15,F'Undermine the credibility of those
OL,16,Fcoming forward'
