OL,7,FWorried staff at fire services in
OL,8,FWales say they feel vindicated by the
OL,9,Ffindings of this new report,
OL,10,Fparticularly about how their
OL,11,Fcomplaints were dealt with.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru Wales,
OL,14,Fwhistleblowers told us when they made
OL,15,Fa complaint about bad behaviour, it
OL,16,Fwas .
