OL,5,Cleadership'
OL,7,FThe committee pointed to various
OL,8,Foccasions where fire leaders "seemed
OL,9,Fto downplay or undermine the
OL,10,Fcredibility of those coming forward as
OL,11,F'settling scores' or waging personal
OL,12,Fvendettas".
