OL,7,FHowever, the report concluded "a lack
OL,8,Fof mutual trust" can have a silencing
OL,9,Feffect on individuals' willingness to
OL,10,F"raise their heads above the parapet".
OL,12,F"Given that some of the more serious
OL,13,Fallegations only came to light as a
OL,14,Fresult of the bravery of
OL,15,Fwhistleblowers, it is crucial that
OL,16,Fevery effort is made to support them
OL,17,Fand staff more generally," the report
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,20,FInterim chief appointment 'reinforces
OL,21,Fnegative perceptions'
