OL,7,FThe Senedd committee heard evidence
OL,8,Ffrom the chief of North Wales Fire
OL,9,Fabout the of Stuart Millington.
OL,11,FThe former assistant chief fire
OL,12,Fofficer in north Wales was promoted to
OL,13,Frun the scandal-hit south Wales
OL,14,Fservice in February 2024 following a
OL,15,Fdamning cultural review. However, days
OL,16,Fafter his appointment, outstanding
OL,17,Fbullying allegations against Mr
OL,18,FMillington, which he denies.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/20
