OL,3,CFire chiefs told to reflect on
OL,4,Cpositions after 'serious failings of
OL,5,Cleadership'
OL,7,FIn Dawn Docx's , she said she saw
OL,8,Fnothing to stop her former assistant
OL,9,Fchief from taking up the new role.
OL,10,FThis was echoed by Dylan Rees, the
OL,11,Ffire authority chair in north Wales,
OL,12,Fwho said: "I didn't see that it
OL,13,Fprecluded the appointment of assistant
OL,14,Fchief officer Stuart Millington."
OL,16,FHowever, the committee says a
OL,17,Fsecretive investigation into the
OL,18,Fallegation against Mr Millington which
OL,19,Fwas "appears at odds with the findings
OL,20,Fof the independent investigator's
OL,21,Freport".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/20
