OL,4,Cpositions after 'serious failings of
OL,5,Cleadership'
OL,7,FThis report later came to light in an
OL,8,Femployment tribunal last month, and
OL,9,Fincluded details of "prima facie
OL,10,Fevidence of bullying and harassment".
OL,12,FThe committee concluded they "found
OL,13,Fthe lack of clarity and the defensive,
OL,14,Fbordering on dismissive, tone of
OL,15,Fseveral individuals responding to
OL,16,Fthese concerns troubling", adding
OL,17,F"staff confidence in the process has
OL,18,Fbeen undermined".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/20
