OL,4,Cpositions after 'serious failings of
OL,5,Cleadership'
OL,7,FThe committee recommend that South
OL,8,FWales Fire and Rescue Service should
OL,9,Fbring in a new permanent chief fire
OL,10,Fofficer "with skills and experiences
OL,11,Ffrom outside the sector in Wales into
OL,12,Fthe key roles responsible for
OL,13,Forganisational culture".
OL,15,FApplications for the appointment of a
OL,16,Fpermanent chief officer or chief
OL,17,Fexecutive for south Wales' service
OL,18,Fclosed last month.
OL,20,F'Some may need to reflect on their
OL,21,Fpositions'
