OL,7,FGoing further, the committee report
OL,8,Fsaid: "Dawn Docx, Cllr Dylan Rees, Dan
OL,9,FStephens and Vij Randeniya all
OL,10,Fdownplayed the allegations" which had
OL,11,Fbeen made against the interim chief in
OL,12,Fsouth Wales.
OL,14,FDan Stephens is the Welsh Government
OL,15,Fadvisor responsible for inspecting
OL,16,Ffire services and was part of the
OL,17,Fappointment of Stuart Millington to
OL,18,Fhis south Wales position.
