OL,3,CFire chiefs told to reflect on
OL,4,Cpositions after 'serious failings of
OL,5,Cleadership'
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Vij Randeniya is the lead
OL,8,FWelsh Government-appointed
OL,9,Fcommissioner in charge of reforming
OL,10,Fthe south Wales service and is
OL,11,Funderstood to have been the person who
OL,12,Ffirst selected Mr Millington for the
OL,13,Finterim role. He is part of a team of
OL,14,Ffour commissioners who were parachuted
OL,15,Fin to oversee the south Wales service
OL,16,Fafter the fire authority was
OL,17,Fdischarged.
