OL,4,Cpositions after 'serious failings of
OL,5,Cleadership'
OL,7,FThe report continues: "This lack of
OL,8,Fcandour is symptomatic of a wider
OL,9,Fcultural problem among fire and rescue
OL,10,Fleaders.
OL,12,F"Given the need to restore confidence,
OL,13,Fparticularly with staff, some may need
OL,14,Fto reflect on their positions."
OL,16,FMatt Wrack, general secretary at the
OL,17,FFire Brigades Union, said: "This
OL,18,Freport confirms serious failings of
OL,19,Fleadership at the very top.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/20
