OL,5,Cleadership'
OL,7,F"Chief fire officers and senior
OL,8,Fmanagers have presided over a
OL,9,Fsituation in which those who speak out
OL,10,Fagainst bullying, harassment and
OL,11,Fdiscrimination are silenced or
OL,12,Fvictimised."
OL,14,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"We will consider the findings
OL,16,Fcarefully as part of a wider programme
OL,17,Fof governance reform and cultural
OL,18,Fimprovement in the fire sector."
