OL,7,FITV Cymru Wales understands Dawn Docx
OL,8,Fwrote to staff on Wednesday on the eve
OL,9,Fof the report's publication to tell
OL,10,Fthem about it. However, she declined
OL,11,Fan interview with ITV about its
OL,12,Ffindings.
OL,14,FBaroness Debbie Wilcox, one of the
OL,15,Fsouth Wales commissioners, said: "We
OL,16,Fwere grateful for the opportunity to
OL,17,Fengage with the committee in an open
OL,18,Fand frank way, and we note its report.
