OL,7,F"Recommendations relating to bringing
OL,8,F'fresh individuals with skills and
OL,9,Fexperiences from outside the sector'
OL,10,Fto the service are an integral part of
OL,11,Four terms of reference and are already
OL,12,Fwell underway.
OL,14,F"The committee's conclusions and
OL,15,Frecommendations about future
OL,16,Fgovernance arrangements are also noted
OL,17,Fand will be helpful in our ongoing
OL,18,Fwork with the cabinet secretary,
OL,19,Fstakeholders, and partners on that
OL,20,Fissue."
